componentInstanceProperties.value:
Company Overview

VentureCrowd is Australia’s leading multi asset digital investment platform democratising access to alternative assets for sophisticated and retail investors who were previously excluded from participating.

In FY23, VentureCrowd members invested $53M in a range of projects generating gross revenue of $5.9M at a gross margin of 36% (more than double the FY22 gross margin). In the same year, we distributed income of $7.6M to investors taking total distributions to $23M since inception.

We have over 74,000 registered members, over 150 portfolio companies and are operating in a market providing strong tailwinds that support our growth. We have proven and delivered our model, and have upgraded our management team to enable future growth.

VentureCrowd is now focused on transforming from a digital market place to a digital platform, and expanding our alternative asset product range and deal flow with a first rate team, ensuring our investor and founder experience is best in market. The next phase of our technology embeds leading edge data and AI tools into the digital investment process, providing greater transactional efficiency for founders and investors, and delivering greater scalability and gross margins for our business.

With this model in place, we will expand into high potential international markets, where there are clear adjacencies for Australian investors.

componentInstanceProperties.value:
The Future of WealthTech is Democratisation



VentureCrowd's mission is to leverage technology to democratise access to capital and investment opportunities, by digitising and streamlining the entire investment process.

We do this by empowering founders and investors with easy to use, leading edge tools to raise capital and make investment decisions.

Our vision is a world where liquidity in the private sector is no longer dominated by the public markets.

The next phase of our technology development, embeds leading edge data and AI tools into our digital investment process, providing greater transactional efficiency for founders and investors, and delivering greater scalability and gross margins for our business.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
The Opportunity

The traditional private capital markets have been highly inefficient for decades, suffering from fragmentation, a lack of transparency, restricted access and ad hoc rules of engagement.

This has made it difficult for the true universe of potential investors to find and invest in deals that are right for them and has artificially reduced the total size of the private capital markets, making capital raising unnecessarily harder than it needs to be.

VentureCrowd's mission is to leverage leading edge technology to digitise the investment process making it easier for founders to raise capital and for investors to participate.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
The Solution

The good news is, the private capital market is undergoing a global digital transformation, giving founders and project promoters more options than ever before for how they raise capital and from whom.

The digitisation of the private capital markets is making it easier to directly connect with a new generation of investors all over the world and generating hundreds of millions of dollars of new capital into the venture capital sector every year with no signs of slowing down.

Our solution is an end-to-end digital investment platform that facilitates the entire investment process, from deal awareness to due diligence, contract execution and portfolio management, with no human interaction.

And we know it works! We have raised over $320M into over 150 ventures since inception, and have provided access to a previously inaccessible range of alternative assets across property, venture capital, private credit and managed fund products to over 74,000 retail and wholesale investors.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
How We're Different

VentureCrowd is much more than just a retail crowdfunding platform or an alternative assets broker with a website. We have deliberately developed a number of unique competitive advantages designed to diversify revenue streams, maximise the market opportunity presented by the digitisation of the private capital markets and position the business for scalable and profitable growth.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
richTextValue
richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Our Technology

VentureCrowd has built proprietary investment technology that digitises the entire investment process, from deal awareness to investment and portfolio management, with no human interaction.

The next phase of our technology roadmap delivers a self-serve campaign management product for founders, syndicate leads and fund managers who are raising capital for their company, property development project, syndicate or fund.

Our new Generative AI-agent, called Sophie, is VentureCrowd’s digital capital raising coach built to guide the user through the entire capital raising journey using 10 years of VentureCrowd campaign management expertise and data.

This new digital product provides a high degree of repeatability, allowing founders to continuously raise capital with an always-on capital railings approach and delivers scalable and high profit revenue.

componentInstanceProperties.value:
Addressable Market

The global alternative assets market is forecast to grow to $24.5 trillion by 2028 at a GACR of 8%, with the private debt component growing at a CAGR of 11% and venture capital at 14%. In Australia, private capital assets under management (AUM) reached a record $118 billion in September 2022, up 21% in 9 months.

The growth is being driven, in part, by growing participation from mainstream investors attracted to the proven benefits of diversification, hedging characteristics, and exposure to higher returns.

Ernst & Young forecasts adoption by mass affluent investors will increase to 32% in 2024, more than double the 2021 figure. Similarly, 53% of financial advisors plan to raise their alternative investments allocations to more than 15% in the next two years, and more than 20% of advisors expect that their alternative investments allocations will be in excess of 25% of their portfolios.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Results So Far

In FY23 VentureCrowd members invested $53,687,057 in a range of projects generating gross revenue of $5,924,371 at a gross margin of 36.21% (more than double the FY22 gross margin).

In the same year, we distributed $7,644,367 to investors taking total distributions to over $23M and total capital raised to over $320M since inception.

VentureCrowd is on track to improve all financial metrics in FY24 and, with the introduction of subscription based revenue, is forecasting even stronger growth in FY25, including a ~96% YoY increase in Gross Revenue and a ~54% increase in Gross Margin.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue

We have upgraded our team, ready for growth.


Our upgraded team uniquely combines strong legal, regulatory & financial services experience together with venture capital, property, funds management and digital product development expertise, bringing together all the complex skills required to deliver this next-generation WealthTech platform.

componentInstanceProperties.value:
Capital Raise

VentureCrowd is currently raising capital through the issue of Convertible Notes to fund the next phase of our platform development and working capital. On completion of the next phase of our platform development we believe the business will have a materially higher valuation.

By the end of FY25, driven by the introduction of our AI-enabled digital capital raising product, we are forecasting gross revenue of $14.5M, generating gross profit of $9M at a gross margin of 62%. At a revenue multiple of between 8 and 15 times revenue, that would value VentureCrowd at between $116M and $217M.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Exit Strategy

In Q3 2025, we intend to position the business for a more substantial growth capital round to fund international expansion. At that time, intend there to be an opportunity for investors in this round to sell their shares (should they wish to) and take advantage of the 25% uplift. By the end of 2025 we expect the business will be well placed for a merger or a trade sale, providing a liquidity opportunity for investors in this round.

The Offer

This is an opportunity to invest in VentreCrowd’s Convertible Note round on the term below.

This round is led by Brisbane venture studio JosephMark, Web3 investment firm Optio Capital and blockchain development firm MakerX as well as a number of high profile individual investors. This round will close as soon as it has been filled.

Why Invest Through VentureCrowd?

VentureCrowd is the leading digital investment platform for alternative assets. We find and fund the brightest and most innovative startups.

Our curation and due diligence is rigorous and our track record of success speaks for itself:

  • Only digital investment platform in Australia to have successfully delivered multiple exit returns to investors through equity crowdfunding.
  • 76K+ members and counting.
  • Over $320,000,000 in capital raised since inception.

VentureCrowd is investor-led, which means we only list deals with secured professional external lead investors. Our investors then invest on the same economic terms as professional investors. If you invest in one of our deals you will receive equity or ownership in the company that is raising the capital. Not only will your investment come with lower fees and capital commitments, but it will also come with reduced deal complexity, and you’ll have access to alternative equity, property and credit opportunities on the same terms as professional lead investors.

Invest now

If you would prefer to speak to one of our team members about this offer, please:

  • email us at hello@venturecrowd.com.au or
  • call us on 1300 039 655

Please note, the Fund Manager reserves the right to vary or cancel the Offer at any time, vary the amount raised under the Offer, vary or waive the Minimum Investment and close the Offer, without notice and without giving reasons.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Risks

Whilst the directors of VentureCrowd are experienced business managers with deep experience in the key areas that are core to the operation of this business, there are always risks associated with investing in venture capital opportunities which may, either directly or indirectly, result in reduced distributions and/or a loss of some of the capital value of an investment in the Fund. Before deciding whether to subscribe for Units, you should consider whether an investment in this Fund is suitable for you and obtain professional advice.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Fees

Investors invest through a VentureCrowd Trust, which VentureCrowd manages as a single asset. We charge an annual management fee to investors, payable on exit and we only charge a performance fee where an exit delivers profit, thereby aligning ourselves with investor outcomes.

  • Contribution Fee: 1.1% This is the fee charged by the Trustee for establishing the Trust and the purchasing entity, structuring the overall investment and raising capital by issuing Units. Payable upon acceptance of your investment by the Trustee.
  • Management Fee: 1.65% per annum (charged on conversion or exit).
  • Performance Fee: 20% of the profit. We only charge a performance fee on conversion or exit.
  • Off Market Transfer Fee (if you wish to transfer your holding to someone else): $500 + 2% of the total amount transferred, unless the buyer is identified by you in advance.

*If the buyer is identified by you in advance the 2% fee does not apply. VentureCrowd cannot guarantee a purchaser for your holding.
